doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    // Required meta tags
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
    // Bootstrap CSS
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css', integrity='sha384-MCw98/SFnGE8fJT3GXwEOngsV7Zt27NXFoaoApmYm81iuXoPkFOJwJ8ERdknLPMO', crossorigin='anonymous')
    // Font Awesome
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.3.1/css/all.css', integrity='sha384-mzrmE5qonljUremFsqc01SB46JvROS7bZs3IO2EmfFsd15uHvIt+Y8vEf7N7fWAU', crossorigin='anonymous')
    // Fuente pacifico
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Pacifico', rel='stylesheet')
    // CSS
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='css/style.css')
    title GuacaBase
  body
    nav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.bg-dark
      a.navbar-brand(href='#') GuacaBase
      button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-toggle='collapse', data-target='#navbarSupportedContent', aria-controls='navbarSupportedContent', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
        span.navbar-toggler-icon
      #navbarSupportedContent.collapse.navbar-collapse
        ul.navbar-nav.mr-auto
          li.nav-item.active
            a.nav-link(href='#')
              | Inicio 
              span.sr-only (current)
          
          li.nav-item.dropdown
            a#navbarDropdown.nav-link.dropdown-toggle(href='#', role='button', data-toggle='dropdown', aria-haspopup='true', aria-expanded='false')
              | Menu
            .dropdown-menu(aria-labelledby='navbarDropdown')
              a.dropdown-item(href='#') Flota
              a.dropdown-item(href='#') Modelos
              .dropdown-divider
              a.dropdown-item(href='#') Destinos
          
        form.form-inline.my-2.my-lg-0
          input.form-control.mr-sm-2(type='search', placeholder='Buscar', aria-label='Search')
          button.btn.btn-outline-primary.my-2.my-sm-0(type='submit') Buscar

    #carouselExampleControls.carousel.slide(data-ride='carousel')
          .carousel-inner
            .carousel-item.active
              img.d-block.w-100(src='https://static.vix.com/es/sites/default/files/imj/nuestrorumbo/5/5-riesgos-de-viajar-en-avion-que-debes-conocer-1.jpg', alt='First slide', style='height:400px')
            
    table
        thead
            tr
                th(scope='col') ID
                th(scope='col') Modelo ID

        tbody
            form(action=`update/${avionSelec.id}` method='POST')
                tr
                    td #{avionSelec.id}
                    td
                        .input-field.col.s12
                            input#moduleID.validate(type='number', value=avionSelec.moduleID, maxlength=3, require, name='moduleID')
                            label(for='moduleID') Ingrese nuevo modelo
                    
                    button.submit(type='submit') Actualizar
    // Bloque
    .row
      .col-1
      // Card
      .col-10
        .card.justify-content-center.mt-2.mb-2(style='background:white')
          ul.list-group.list-group-flush
            li.list-group-item
              h3.float-center Sobre Nosotros
            p.m-2
              | Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Rem quos, nesciunt labore voluptate ducimus accusantium modi saepe possimus architecto, quo tenetur, dolorum autem deleniti delectus doloribus vero aliquid! Soluta, asperiores?
      .col-1

      .row(style='background:primary')
        .col-4
          li  
        .col-4
        .col-4
